{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_06a120636f494a29a0fa5b9a","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Bitcart\n2\t\n3\t![Github All Contributors](https://img.shields.io/github/all-contributors/bitcart/bitcart?style=flat-square)\n4\t[![CI](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n5\t![Codecov](https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/bitcart/bitcart?style=flat-square)\n6\t[![Python versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/bitcart?style=flat-square)](https://docs.bitcart.ai)\n7\t\n8\tBitcart is a platform for merchants, users and developers which offers easy setup and use.\n9\t\n10\t## Linked repositories\n11\t\n12\tOur ecosystem consists of a few packages, this is our central repository.\n13\t\n14\tIt is recommended to propose feature requests to Bitcart ecosystem as a whole on that repository.\n15\t\n16\tFull list of our repositories:\n17\t\n18\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart - Bitcart Core Daemons and Merchants API\n19\t\n20\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-admin - The admin panel of Bitcart\n21\t\n22\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-store - Bitcart ready store\n23\t\n24\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-docker - Docker packaging, base for all deployment methods\n25\t\n26\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-sdk - Python library for coins connection\n27\t\n28\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitccl - The BitCCL scripting language for checkout flow automation\n29\t\n30\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-docs - [Bitcart documentation](https://docs.bitcart.ai)\n31\t\n32\thttps://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-site - [Bitcart official site](https://bitcart.ai)\n33\t\n34\t## Docs\n35\t\n36\tDocs are available at https://docs.bitcart.ai or in our [docs repository](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart-docs)\n37\t\n38\t## Contributing\n39\t\n40\tSee [our contributing guidelines](https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) for details.\n41\t\n42\t## Contributors ✨\n43\t\n44\tThanks goes to these wonderful people ([emoji key](https://allcontributors.org/docs/en/emoji-key)):\n45\t\n46\t<!-- ALL-CONTRIBUTORS-LIST:START - Do not remove or modify this section -->\n47\t<!-- prettier-ignore-start -->\n48\t<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n49\t<table>\n50\t  <tbody>\n51\t    <tr>\n52\t      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/MrNaif2018\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/39452697?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"MrNaif2018\"/><br /><sub><b>MrNaif2018</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"#maintenance-MrNaif2018\" title=\"Maintenance\">🚧</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=MrNaif2018\" title=\"Code\">💻</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=MrNaif2018\" title=\"Documentation\">📖</a> <a href=\"#design-MrNaif2018\" title=\"Design\">🎨</a></td>\n53\t      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/tomasmor42\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/42064734?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"tomasmor42\"/><br /><sub><b>tomasmor42</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=tomasmor42\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n54\t      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/yagicandegirmenci\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/62724709?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Yağız Değirmenci\"/><br /><sub><b>Yağız Değirmenci</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=yagicandegirmenci\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n55\t      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"14.28%\"><a href=\"https://github.com/xiaoxianma\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/3086064?v=4?s=100\" width=\"100px;\" alt=\"Weidong Sun\"/><br /><sub><b>Weidong Sun</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcart/bitcart/commits?author=